         printf("This is your next step you need to make a choice 1\nChoice 1: You seem to make good money from your fan and support, you go all out with your spending\n and hope of making enough fans to have a consistent income to play for your everyday needs and game. \nChoice 2: You decided to keep spending the same amount of money, and make no changes. \nChoice 3: You went outside and saw the condition of the world, the homeless, \nand the lack of food for the children and you decided to put your money into donations.\n\n");
        printf("Make your choice to determain you future: 1, 2, or 3\n");
