//Ending (9)
void end1(){
    printf("You seem to be doing good and you want more money. \nYou went out of your way to make sure your content is the best and would do anything to get your viewer. \nBut the worst thing happens when your viewer sees the visible change in your personality. \nThey notice that you were not the person they are use too. You soo lost many viewer, \nand soon your back in square one. Don’t be too greedy, \nbetter luck next time try again.");
