void end9(){
    printf("You want to reach your dream but you are not really putting time into it, so you decided to give your \naccount to another person to play it for you and they soon reach to be number one on the leaderboard. \nYou did that and claimed that all the work was yours and they stole the account. \nYou somehow got the account back, too bad the game dev did this and took back the account and returned it back to the rightful owner. \nThey then proceeded to ban you from ever playing the game again, and even if you somehow got back they’ll track your account and ban it. \nMoral of the story is don't play dirty or bypass the system. Try again.");
